      "content": "everything just feels so quiet lately. i spend 10 hours a day staring at a screen in this apartment and the only time anyone interacts with me is through a slack notification or a brief email. sometimes i look at the city lights outside and it hits me that i'm basically just a ghost in the machine. like... if i just stopped showing up, would anyone even realize i was gone?",
